description: Jada hates these kind of parties. It was always just top executives flaunting their newest arm candy to their friends. But being signed to the label she has no choice. She hooks up with a big name producer, who represents some of the biggest artists in Hollywood, and after he gives her his card to discuss her career, she doesn't waste any time meeting up to get to know each other better.
